text: Ali Amzad Government Girls' High School () is a public secondary school located at Maulvibazar Sadar Upazila, Moulvibazar in Sylhet, Bangladesh. ==About== == References == Category:High schools in Bangladesh Category:Schools in Moulvibazar District Category:Moulvibazar Sadar Upazila
